How many times you've reached Sector 8. Challenge levels are unlocked if higher than 1. Leah starts spawning if higher than 1, and CURA starts spawning if higher than 2.
How many Renegade Cruisers you've killed. Unlocks the Mysterious Beacon when talking to the judges if 5 or higher.
How many times you've plucked the orchid children in Gathering Sectors. The Sapling Protection Service starts appearing in the orchid field event if 5 or higher.
If you've started dylan's quest. The quest is started if greater than 1, increasing prof_dylan_counter with each run started.
A counter for dylan's quest. Increases with each run started if prof_dylan_met is greater than 1, and dylan will reroute you into Hoedown if greater than 3.
If you have completed dylan's quest. The quest is given if set to 0, and dylan's shop will be greatly discounted if 1 or higher. MV: Hoedown is also unlocked in the jukebox if 1 or higher.
If you've opened up the nexus pod in the Hektar Mega-Market. The password will be there if 1 or higher, otherwise either Obyn or Anurak are needed.
How many times you've met the judges. The judges will give a scrap + weapon reward instead of giving access to a boon if this is set to 0.
If you talked to Thest and gotten a boon from them last time you visited the judges. Thest is unavailable if 1 or higher.
If you talked to Wakeson and gotten a boon from them last time you visited the judges. Wakeson is unavailable if 1 or higher.
If you talked to Corby and gotten a boon last time you visited the judges. Corby is unavailable if 1 or higher.
Challenge level of the run/selected challenge levels for future runs. 0 is casual, 1 is standard, 2 is challenge, 3 is extreme.
If you've died to TOWR before unlocking chaos mode. A cultist ship that gives you the reroute to fight TOWR spawns in Sector 8 if set to 1 or higher.
If chaos mode is unlocked. The gnome appears if this is set to 1 or higher.
If the magical hat is unlocked. The option to take the hat in the hangar is available if set to 1 or higher.
What the toggle hotkey is set to. Set to 91 ("[") by default. Uses ASCII to convert the variable to the key.
What the storage hotkey is set to. Set to 93 ("]") by default.
If the mysterious beacon is unlocked. The option to activate it is available if set to 1 or higher.
If you've given scrap to the great eye. 15 scrap will be given to you in the great eye event if set to 1 or higher.
